Dutch
David Burke is een kleinschalige drugsdealer die het houdt bij het handelen met

leien dakje, tot hij onverwachts genoodzaakt is voor het grote geld te gaan.

English
After being robbed of a week's take, small-time pot dealer David is forced by
his boss to go to Mexico to pick up a load of marijuana. In order to improve his
odds of making it past the border, David asks the broke stripper Rose and two
local teenagers to join him and pretend they're on a family holiday.
